<h2>Sign Up For HSFCU’s eStatements! </h2>
<p>Still waiting for paper account statements to arrive by regular mail? eStatements are a better option. </p>
 
<p>Our eStatements are paperless account statements that are displayed online within our secure Online Banking service. You get your account information much sooner, and more:</p>
<ul>
	<li>eStatements are FREE!</li>
    <li>eStatements eliminate clutter – They can be saved onto your computer for easy reference when needed.</li>
    <li>eStatements are less vulnerable to identity thieves – They won’t sit in your mailbox when you’re working, running errands or on vacation.</li>
    <li>eStatements help the environment – They conserve water, electricity and trees, and reduce environmental pollution from the chemicals used in paper manufacturing.</li>
</ul>

 
<p>Sign up for eStatements today, and do something good for yourself and the environment! To get started, use the Online Banking link above.</p>
